name: one-dork-syntax
description: One Dork syntax theme for Atom (based on One Dark)
readme:
# Offshoot of Atom's one dark syntax theme.

See [oceans16-bright](https://github.com/dunovank/oceans16-bright-syntax) and [grade3](https://github.com/dunovank/grade3-syntax) for more Atom themes or go check out my [jupyter-themes](https://github.com/dunovank/jupyter-themes) repository 
  to use this theme in your Jupyter Notebooks.
